OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fdry with some brightness at first
OL,7,Fbefore rain spreads northeast through
OL,8,Fthe evening and overnight, becoming
OL,9,Fdry with clear spells by morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FIt will be dry and warm
OL,12,Fthrough the day with some prolonged
OL,13,Fbright or hazy sunny spells.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarm
OL,16,Ffrom Sunday to Tuesday with some
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells, chance of some
OL,18,Frain later on Sunday. Perhaps a bit
OL,19,Fcloudier and cooler on Tuesday.
